{"tid":900664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 瘋狂BT?】Google遭劫持 流量突轉向中國和俄羅 搜尋引擎、雲端服務受干擾","createTime":"2018-11-13T12:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T12:16:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a15e7804bcb3f81fea92646c9d7778162036678f","tid":900664,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"美聯社報道，互聯網巨擘Google於當地時間周一（12日）下午，遭到「互聯網流量劫持」（Internet traffic hijacking）干擾，多個服務受影響，包括搜尋引擎和雲端服務。<br />\n<br />\n互聯網流量劫持是指黑客利用惡意軟件修改瀏覽器、鎖定主頁或不停彈出新視窗，強迫網絡使用者訪問特定網站，導致用戶流量流失。有網絡監察公司表示，今次干擾為時長達近2小時，Google的用戶流量突然轉向中國和俄羅斯的電訊公司，於下午5時半左右才結束。<br />\n<br />\n網絡情報公司ThousandEyes管理人員岩根（Alex Henthorn-Iwane）表示，今次事件是其公司歷來監察中，影響Google最嚴重的一次。如此的流量劫持可助長間諜行為和金融盜竊，亦可令重要的服務癱瘓。岩根認為，今次可能是某一個國家針對流量劫持的一次實戰演習。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle其後證實事件，表示相信是源於外來因素。美國國土安全部則暫未回應傳媒查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181113/bkn-20181113100527397-1113_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181113%2Fbkn-20181113100527397-1113_00822_001.html&d=PYL5ImRlc6bw7cq%2Be%2BrcizPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0ac850a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181113/bkn-20181113100527397-1113_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f036ae397a60db544335e27c932d64de50ef9fa6","tid":900664,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ddaf59644b5ab1c6fa48a3ebfb54d9dcbebfb2","tid":900664,"uid":81518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f43c0f7b1805e99ddb7d3c1d636349ac0af255b2","tid":900664,"uid":39200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"準備打網絡戰？ D華為小米設備又助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c240087df82d5531e392b248046d5dca6c9080","tid":900664,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:13:54.000Z","msg":"Google加緊server去大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3044367f800c4fa92df359fcacf517eb4f49fc37","tid":900664,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f43c0f7b1805e99ddb7d3c1d636349ac0af255b2","tid":900664,"uid":39200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"準備打網絡戰？ D華為小米設備又助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T12:16:27.000Z","msg":"我和殭屍路由器有個約會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}